      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Samuel_Bak.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/ce/Samuel_Bak.jpg/330px-Samuel_Bak.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"197\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/ce/Samuel_Bak.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Samuel_Bak.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Samuel Bak</div></div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samuel_Bak\">Samuel Bak</a>, (born August 12, 1933)<br />\na Polish born American painter and writer who survived the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Holocaust\">Holocaust</a> and immigrated to Israel in 1948. Since 1993, he has lived in the United States. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Links\">Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Category:Samuel_Bak&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chgs.elevator.umn.edu/asset/viewAsset/57f3b6787d58ae5f74bf8ba9#57f3b6d77d58ae5574bf8bcf\">Chess in the Art of Samuel Bak</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chgs.elevator.umn.edu/\">Center for Holocaust &amp; Genocide Studies</a>, <a href=\"/University_of_Minnesota\" title=\"University of Minnesota\">University of Minnesota</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.puckergallery.com/artists/#/samuel-bak/\">Samuel Bak represented by Pucker Gallery since 1969</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://valsur.livejournal.com/129416.html\">Шахматы в искусстве (22 часть) BAK Samuel</a> by Valerij Surkov</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301032130\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.060 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.595 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:1193-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301032129 and revision id 15244\n -->\n"
